HEADWORD: gratifying
<hw>gratifying</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>giving personal
satisfaction.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> appreciated, pleasing, satisfying.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>occasioning pride; <as>as, a <ex>gratifying</ex>
