[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>pleasing to the mind or feeling.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> sweet.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>4.</sn> <def>affording pleasure or satisfaction.</def>⟦br⟧
